'''The 1939 Summer Deaflympics''' officially known as 5th Summer Deaflympics is an international multi-sport event that was held from 24 August 1939 to 27 August 1939. This event was hosted by [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.deaflympics.com/games.asp?1939-s|title=Games {{!}} Deaflympics|website=www.deaflympics.com|language=en|access-date=2017-08-30}}</ref>
