{{italic title}}
'''''Avtomanija''''' is the leading [[Slovene language|Slovene]] automobile [[internet portal]] and magazine (2005-2010). The content is divided between [[automotive]] news, vehicle reviews, and [[motorsports]] coverage. Originally only a motoring website since 1998, expanded to magazine publishing in 2005. In the 2006, under the direction of longtime editor [[Artur Švarc]], changed its name from ''Avtomania'' to ''Avtomanija'', 32 page magazine published weekly. Name was changed due incorrect spelling of the word, which was in original partially English and partially Slovenian. ''Avtomanija'' was up to date Slovenia's only weekly automotive magazine.

